rop guardian armor (/rude) which is what the guardian mobs drop.<br>
<br>
Ry'Gorr armor is also good.  I'll assume you have full ranger quest armor from wherever it is you get it...temple sol ro maybe?  Darkmail gloves are super cheap from the frenzy camp in lguk.  You can get engraved bone pauldrons pretty cheap (12ac 3agl 5dex neg20 cha) shoulders (the quest that generates them is currently broken).<br>
<br>
Getting the ranger armor from Kunark would be the next step after the above goals.  It's got higher AC than just about anything else you can get, and useful spell effects for the most part.<br>
<br>
I'm not sure what jewelry you are wearring, but cheap good stuff you can get for a few hundred PP is the 6ac 65hp rings, blue diamond/regular diamond rings for resists, blue diamond earrings for resists, black sapphire earrings for 2ac 35hp 25mana.  You can get a decent 7ac 13wis 13int neck if you can get on a fire giant raid.  When I do FGs, my group looks for (no offense intended here) some noob in zone to loot them if they should happen to drop (no drop).  You can probably pick up a Larikan's mask from Seb for about 200P or so (6ac 10charge sup camo).  Sarnak Hide mask at 6ac 5str is probably the next mask you'd be looking for.  For range slot you can probably get the medicine totem on your own (5ac 5wis).<br>
<br>
This leaves your weapons.  I don't think the wurmslayer is a bad choice of a weapon for your level.  It's pretty cheap.  Besides that, there's really no intermediate 1h slashers besides the velium weapons that will be a decent trasition from yaks to 1:2 ratio weapons like lammy, lupine dagger, jade mace (even though you can't equip.  just listing for example sake), or CSS.  Those all run about 10k in price on average, give or take a few K.  You might want a sword of skyfire, but be damn careful in how you use it.  Enchanters will hate you, and so will your cleric if you don't have good fire resist.  There's also another cursed sword that's about 1:2 ratio that procs cancel magic on yourself.  If you have something that produces an instant icon on yourself (like bracer of hidden, or shrunken goblin skull earring, or jboots) you can use it with fair success. <p>=============================
<br>Juujuu Bigmojo
<br>60 Halfling Shaman
